10:50.984 --> 10:52.583
(chair rattles)

10:52.653 --> 10:54.452
- Really?
- Really. You free right now?

10:54.587 --> 10:56.021
- As a bird. What're we doing?

10:56.156 --> 10:59.023
- Boosting a truck.
- In! (chuckles)

11:00.861 --> 11:02.827
