13:13.660 --> 13:15.560
- I don't believe you!

13:15.695 --> 13:17.228
- Is something wrong, davide?

13:17.297 --> 13:19.563
- Yeah, dave, what seems
to be the problem now?

13:19.565 --> 13:22.033
- He prefers da-vide.

13:22.102 --> 13:24.335
